tagWord.text: According to my precise calculations, this Operator will be of great help to you, Doctor!
By the way, Doctor, how about becoming a VIP? Take advantage of this cost-effective service and free up some of that budget for Rhodes Island!
These new arrivals were specifically picked out for the Operators of Rhodes Island. Hopefully the real products look like they do in these pictures… Ugh…
Here's the pack the Procurement Department prepared for you! Please take it! Well, it's from the Procurement Department and they need you to pay for it.
Are you going to give this outfit to Hibiscus yourself, Doctor?
Don’t miss this limited-time sale! The hottest fashion upgrades for your Operators have arrived!
A new furniture collection just came in! Turn your dorm into that getaway you’ve always dreamed of!

Aren't these inspired outfits just drop dead gorgeous? You still have to pay for them, but don't let that stop you!
This fierce style absolutely stole my heart! I'm not sure if our not-so-brave Operators will be able to sleep at night though...
Feel the rustic charm of a country fireplace, right here at Rhodes Island! You wouldn't want to miss this opportunity!
High mountains! Dense forests! Arid deserts! Doctor, your Operators are already dying to try it on.
The staff of Penguin Logistics proposed a dormitory ambience improvement plan! I prepared the list just for you, Doctor!
These outfits are masterpieces from the finest Victorian tailors. Does anyone feel like sending me one?
Rhodes Island's elite workstation is now available! Work like a pro - start by remodeling your dormitory!
You won't find more exclusive outfits than these, Doctor! Even if you don't plan on letting your Operators wear these, you should buy them anyway as an investment!
The New Year is here once again, Doctor! I've added a ton of new products to my collection - care to take a look?
The New Year is here once again, Doctor! I've added a ton of new products to my collection - care to take a look?
Happy half year anniversary! To celebrate the occasion, I've prepared a special gift for you! May each anniversary be filled with fortune!
Happy half year anniversary! Why don't you just purchase one of these outfits to celebrate the anniversary?
After a one-time payment, you can enjoy Lungmen's distinctive food right here on this very ship!
Brand new outfit, brand new you! Everyone wants a share of the good luck!
Opulent furniture! Sophisticated décor! Even if you're just looking at the piano, it's already worth taking out that wallet!
There's an event going on at the cafeteria right now. Plenty of food and drinks, and they're even giving out prizes! These three are the favorites to win - who do you think stands the best chance?
Those girls sure were in a hurry to replicate their school clubroom… Think it's out of a sense of nostalgia? They must have made some great memories.
High mountains! Dense forests! Arid deserts! Doctor, your Operators are already dying to try it on.
With this authentic L.G.D. office set, anyone can experience what it's like to be a police chief. You better take me in when nobody's looking!

These luxurious outfits were meticulously crafted by designers with no budget constraints. Perhaps next time, the Procurement Division will also try purchasing them up without considering the expense… Actually, forget it. Kalt'sit would get mad.
A house that gives you a view of the night like this would cost a fortune in Leithania. Luckily, you can achieve the same thing here at a fraction of the cost.
An outfit made from Grani's recollections. We tried to connect her with a designer to make this possible, and here are the fruits of that work.
Don't you hate it when you let a promotion slide by? I know that feeling all too well! Luckily for you, Doctor, you have another chance!
Oh, are you a Rhodes Island Operator? One pizza to Closure's room, please and thank you.
I have no idea which cities the "Seven Cities" are supposed to be, but the food and drinks here are must-try. Good enough to convince me to leave this sunless den, *hic*…

As thanks for your dedicated service these last months, the Procurement Division has prepared these special discounts just for you! Seriously, they're great deals, I even had to use some of the money I set aside for a new graphics card to make these deals possible... *sniffle*

Don't worry, Doctor! Everything here, especially the walls, has been treated and won't collapse even in case of explosion! You can always trust my engineering prowess!

tagWord.text: Please show your support to your favorite artist by purchasing their themed furniture. If you love 'em all, then take everything home!

While away from the cities, outfit is everything. Looking good is one thing, but practicality matters more. Understood?
I heard that Yen people would decorate their rooms like this during festivals. Warfarin will definitely love everything being red.
If you like the outfits you wore when experiencing the escape game, you can visit me to purchase it.
Whislash treats the younger generation of her family with great care. I wish I had an aunt just like her.

welcomeWords.text: What can I get for you, Doc?

clickWords.text: The Procurement Department has everything you need. Take your time.
Pro Tip: This is all great stuff worth taking home!
No questions. I'll only tell you to buy it all!
The Procurement Department can get you anything on the shopping list.
So close, yet so far. You're right in front of me, but I can't afford to buy you.
That's the best deal we can get, Doctor! Stop asking!
I'll take them if you don't.
